              <ptr target="bib:Lakshmana_Rao1930"></ptr>
            </bibl> initially thought.</note>
        </p>
        <p n="10">
          <note>The word <foreign xml:lang="san-Latn">iti</foreign> should logically be placed after the second order (<foreign xml:lang="san-Latn">parihārttavyā</foreign>) in line 12.</note>
        </p>
      </div>
